The truth is like the sun. The closer you look, the more it blinds.

1. the +比较级, the +比较级

  The more he said, the angrier he became. 他说的越多越生气。
  The younger you are, the easier it is to learn. 越年轻，学起来越容易。
  
2.blind
  2.1 失明的
  2.2 对..视而不见的   be blind (to xx)
  David's good looks and impeccable manners had always made her blind to his faults.
  戴维英俊的长相和完美的举止总是让她对他的缺点视而不见。
  
  2.3 the blind 盲人
  
  He was a teacher of the  blind.  他曾教过盲人。
  
  
